PN,43201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,FStructural damage to an apartment
OL,8,Fblock in Plymouth was known about in
OL,9,FDecember last year - but the owners
OL,10,Fdid not feel an evacuation was
OL,11,Fnecessary until last week, ITV West
OL,12,FCountry can reveal.
OL,14,FResidents were given one hour's notice
OL,15,Fto leave their flats at Evolution Cove
OL,16,Fin Stonehouse on Friday March 20th.
OL,18,FMany are still in temporary
OL,19,Faccommodation, and have been told it
OL,20,Fcould be up to eight weeks until they
OL,21,Fcan return.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,FThe company which owns the building
OL,8,Fsays its top priority is the safety
OL,9,Fand wellbeing of residents.
OL,11,F'We were shellshocked'
OL,13,FSophie Hocking and her partner were
OL,14,Fweeks away from moving house when they
OL,15,Fwere told to leave.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,FThey enlisted friends and family to
OL,8,Fhastily pack up furniture and
OL,9,Fbelongings, not knowing where they
OL,10,Fwould go or what would happen next.
OL,11,F"Stressful doesn't even cover it,"
OL,12,FSophie said.
OL,14,F"I'm not sure we've ever been so
OL,15,Fstressed in our lives to be honest. We
OL,16,Fwere completely shellshocked.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,F"We've been very fortunate with where
OL,8,Fwe've been staying, however there's
OL,9,Fnothing that takes away the lack of
OL,10,Fnotice and the pure panic that sets
OL,11,Fin."
OL,13,FThe reason for the urgent evacuation
OL,14,Fwas a crack in a structural beam in
OL,15,Fthe building's car park.
OL,17,FWe can reveal that this was first
OL,18,Funcovered back in December last year,
OL,19,Fbut at that point the building's owner
OL,20,Fsaid their advice was not to evacuate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,FLast week new information came to
OL,8,Flight, meaning the building was 'at
OL,9,Frisk of collapse' and everybody had to
OL,10,Fleave.
OL,12,F"We could have had more warning on
OL,13,FFriday so that children weren't in bed
OL,14,Fand people had time to evacuate their
OL,15,Fhomes in daylight," Sophie added.
OL,17,F"This has been going on for months,
OL,18,Fthese cracks aren't new.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,F"There have been lots of people
OL,8,Fsurveying down there for a while. So
OL,9,Fsurely it's just a waiting game.
OL,11,F"I'm not an expert, but it feels as if
OL,12,Fsomebody has not properly done their
OL,13,Fjob."
OL,15,F'They keep changing the goalposts'
OL,17,FDad Jon Dingle was among those who had
OL,18,Fto leave thier homes, he is now in a
OL,19,Ftwo-bedroom apartment in the Keyham
OL,20,Farea of the city, his third temporary
OL,21,Fhome in the space of a week.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,F"I was put into a hotel for that first
OL,8,Fnight. Then the second night, they
OL,9,Fmoved me into a little bedsit which
OL,10,Fwasn't ideal," Jon said.
OL,12,F"Luckily they got me out of that
OL,13,Fbedsit into the property where I am
OL,14,Fnow.
OL,16,F"Which I'm grateful for, it's a two-
OL,17,Fbedroom property, and at least I can
OL,18,Fcook my own food and I've got my own
OL,19,Fbedroom and my son's got a bedroom
OL,20,Fhere and all that type of stuff.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,F"But yeah it's still not home. I'm
OL,8,Fliving out of a suitcase and just
OL,9,Ffeeling very unsettled at the moment."
OL,11,FResidents are receiving regular
OL,12,Fupdates from the building owners and
OL,13,Fmanagers - the latest is that it's
OL,14,Flikely to be six to eight weeks until
OL,15,Fthey can return.
OL,17,FJon said: "They keep changing the
OL,18,Fgoalposts. To start with it was four
OL,19,Fweeks, then it went up to six weeks,
OL,20,Fand now apparently it's eight weeks.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,F"It is worrying not knowing if we're
OL,8,Fgoing to get an e-mail at some point
OL,9,Fto say suddenly it's ten weeks or
OL,10,Ftwelve weeks. We just don't know."
OL,12,F'We understand the distress and
OL,13,Fdifficulty this has caused'
OL,15,FA Grey GR spokesperson said: "Grey
OL,16,FGR's top priority is the safety and
OL,17,Fwellbeing of residents.
OL,19,F"On 20 March, our structural engineers
OL,20,Freviewed the structural issues that
OL,21,Fwere first noted in December 2025.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,F"In December, the advice was that
OL,8,Fthere was no requirement to evacuate.
OL,10,F"New information received on 20 March
OL,11,Fshowed the issues to be more complex
OL,12,Fthan first thought, requiring more
OL,13,Fextensive work to remedy, and
OL,14,Frequiring immediate evacuation.
OL,16,F"Grey GR acted on this advice and
OL,17,Fasked residents to evacuate on the
OL,18,Fsame day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,F"We are providing alternative
OL,8,Faccommodation, working with all
OL,9,Fresidents to ensure this is suitable,
OL,10,Fand covering these costs.
OL,12,F"Grey GR's team has been, and will
OL,13,Fcontinue to be, in frequent contact
OL,14,Fwith residents, including 1 to 1
OL,15,Fmeetings, online group meetings and
OL,16,Fphone calls, and has a dedicated
OL,17,Fsupport line available.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,F"We understand the distress and
OL,8,Fdifficulty this has caused and are
OL,9,Fthankful to residents for working
OL,10,Falongside us during this time.
OL,12,F"Our goal is to allow residents to
OL,13,Freturn to their properties as soon as
OL,14,Fit is safe to do so. In the meantime,
OL,15,Fit is important that residents do not
OL,16,Freturn to Evolution Cove."
OL,18,F'We cannot take risks with your lives'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774634759
OL,3,CStructural damage to 'unsafe'
OL,4,Capartment block was known about three
OL,5,Cmonths ago
OL,7,FLuke Pollard, Labour MP for Plymouth
OL,8,FSutton and Devonport, said: "I want to
OL,9,Fthank the residents who have already
OL,10,Ffollowed the safety protocols during
OL,11,Fthis incredibly difficult time.
OL,13,F"My ask to you is simple: please take
OL,14,Fup the offer of alternative
OL,15,Faccommodation.
OL,17,F"Even if you feel your individual flat
OL,18,Fis fine, the structural integrity of
OL,19,Fthe whole building is the concern, and
OL,20,Fwe cannot take risks with your lives."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
